Class MoneyMarket

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.Account
com.example.project3.Savings
com.example.project3.MoneyMarket
public class MoneyMarket
extends Savings
This is the MoneyMarket class responsible for all MoneyMarket accounts. It has the capacity to get the monthly interest, fees, and the type of account
Author:
